WHAT IS IT?
-----------

  'Columnar' is a Workbench game where the goal is to make the
roof fall by lowering the support columns... That sounds simple?
As the proverbial catchphrase, so to speak, is: there is a catch.
As you click on columns in order to lower them, other columns
randomly get higher, unless they reach the roof...

  If you click on an empty space over a column, that column will
get higher, but another column will decrease in height... When the
topmost portions of all columns are separated from the roof, the
roof will drop by one level. Continue in lowering the roof until
it gets to the same level as the platforms that are located on
either side of the game board...

  Complete the game in the least amount of moves.

  Have fun!

